sequenceDiagram
  %% 現状の1回の memory query シーケンス図: Mermaid UML sequenceDiagramで相互作用を見る

  actor User as 人 / Codex
  participant RX as research_x
  participant Policy as SearchLens / ObjectiveRoutePolicy
  participant Routes as Route Portfolio
  participant Guard as ProviderApiBudgetGuard
  participant Evidence as Source Bundle / Context / Citation
  participant Authority as AnswerAuthorityGatekeeper
  participant Boundary as Answer Boundary
  participant Trace as Workflow Trace

  User->>RX: 質問・目的・context budget
  RX->>Trace: sidecar trace を開始
  RX->>Policy: 関心・制約・保存可否を整理
  Policy->>Routes: local / media / provider候補ルートを選ぶ

  par local lanes
    Routes-->>Routes: exact / SQLite FTS / BM25 / metadata / relation
  and provider-backed lanes
    Routes->>Guard: semantic / OCR / Reader / rerank / LLM-context を確認
    Guard-->>Trace: provider_gated または実行可を記録
  end

  Routes-->>RX: candidates と skip reason
  RX->>Evidence: Source Bundle / Context Chunk / Citationへ復元
  Evidence->>Authority: claim support を確認
  Authority->>Boundary: answer support または停止理由
  Boundary-->>RX: answer / needs_review / source_not_restored / citation_missing / hypothesis_only / provider_gated
  RX->>Trace: route・guard・evidence・stop reasonを保存
  RX-->>User: status・citations・traceを返す
